overview: Syren De Mer suggests her stepdaughter, Elena Koshka, that it might be a good idea to try on a couple of dresses before choosing the one. She can't help but look at her and see how much she's grown. She's a woman now and Syren couldn't be any prouder. She also can't help but notice the curves of her thighs, how her breasts perk up.
title: My Daughter's Engaged
